ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project performs complete end-to-end Sentiment Analysis on the IMDB 50K Movie Reviews Dataset using Natural Language Processing (NLP), Data Mining techniques, and Machine Learning models.

The goal is to classify movie reviews as Positive or Negative using multiple algorithms and visualize the entire workflow in a professional Jupyter Notebook pipeline.

