ğŸ“Š Algorithms Used
Category	Techniques
NLP	Tokenization, Stopwords Removal, Lemmatization
Vectorization	TF-IDF, N-Grams
Classification Models	Logistic Regression, Naive Bayes, Linear SVM, Random Forest, Decision Tree, Gradient Boosting
Evaluation	Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1 Score, Confusion Matrix
Data Mining	Word Frequency, Topic Modeling (LDA)
